name: WA Ferries
tagline: Washington State Ferries Schedules On Your Wrist
body:
## About
Get departure times for all Washington State ferries on your Pebble. Check real-time alerts. Pin departure times to your timeline so you never forget!

Check it out on the [Pebble App Store](https://apps.getpebble.com/en_US/application/57091fd38448d8e6e4000026).

## Release Notes
#### Version 1.0
* Ferry Schedules!
* Pin departure times to timeline!
* Check route Alerts!
